Russian. but not
limited to that.

217
00:11:22.464 --> 00:11:24.031
This is a mole hunt.

218
00:11:24.205 --> 00:11:26.381
I... I don't like that word.

219
00:11:26.642 --> 00:11:28.470
Makes this sound
